      • setCampaignDialogsEnabled

        public static Engage setCampaignDialogsEnabled(boolean enabled)
        Enables or disables campaign dialogs in the app. Individual campaign dialogs may be handled separately by implementing CampaignTriggerListener

        Campaign dialogs are enabled by default

        Parameters:
        enabled - true to enable Campaign dialogs.
